    "description": "文化是一個複合體，包括知識、信仰。藝術、道德、法律、風俗以及人類在社會裡獲得的一切能力與習慣。本課程是要從人類文化中研究語言。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.了解何謂語言<br>2.了解何謂文化<br>3.探討語言與文化的關係<br>4.從語詞的語源和變遷看過去文化的遺跡<br>5.從造詞心理看民族的文化程度<br>6.從借字看文化的接觸<br>7.從英語和美語之間的差異分析英美的文化習慣<br>",
        "en": "1.Understand what a language is <br>2.Understand what a culture is <br>3.Discuss the relationship between languages and cultures <br>4.Viewing the relics of past cultures from the etymology and changes of words  <br>5.Viewing the  National Culture Level from the Psychology of Word Creation <br>6.Analysis of British and American Cultural Habits from the Differences Between English and American <br>"
